## Reference editors (copy, donвЂ™t invent)

For hard playback/scrub/sync problems on this stack, study how existing editors
solved it (see also `preview-playback-architecture.mdc` for the browser path):

- **Shotcut / MLT** вЂ” consumer refresh while paused, audio clock while playing.
- **elah, nimone/fast-video-cut** вЂ” frame copy-out, decode-ahead, no seek spam.
- **CapCut / Resolve / Premiere** вЂ” proxies in background, dynamic scrub defers
  exact frames; never block the user on a full transcode.

When ANY hard problem appears, reference an existing editor first. We do not
invent novel approaches in the video-editing core.
